* 2001年[[九一一恐怖襲擊事件|九一一恐怖襲擊事件]]：美國政府一直聲稱此事件是由基地组织策動，基地組織最早否認這一指控。但随后的情报资料，包括基地组织的文件、[[录像带|录像带]]、[[磁带|磁带]]记录，加上本·拉登后来發表聲明承認自己策划<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/bin-laden-claims-responsibility-for-9-11-1.513654|language=en|title=Bin Laden claims responsibility for 9/11|publisher=CBCNEWS|date=2004-10-29|accessdate=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607123146/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/bin-laden-claims-responsibility-for-9-11-1.513654|archive-date=2017-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，显示本·拉登可能参与了这一行动的策划。然而FBI官員在2006年表示无足夠证据证明本·拉登涉案<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenewamerican.com/usnews/crime/item/7474-why-was-9-11-not-mentioned-on-osama-wanted-poster|language=en|title=Why Was 9/11 Not Mentioned on Osama Wanted Poster?|publisher=The New American|date=2011-05-06|accessdate=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222103314/http://www.thenewamerican.com/usnews/crime/item/7474-why-was-9-11-not-mentioned-on-osama-wanted-poster|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rextomb">{{cite web|url=http://www.historycommons.org/entity.jsp?entity=rex_tomb_1|title=Profile: Rex Tomb|publisher=History Commons|accessdate=2017-06-02|quote=The reason why 9/11 is not mentioned on Osama bin Laden’s Most Wanted page is because the FBI has no hard evidence connecting bin Laden to 9/11.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229020535/http://www.historycommons.org/entity.jsp?entity=rex_tomb_1|archive-date=2016-12-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此始终没有正式起诉本·拉登。<ref name="ibtimes2011">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/osama-bin-laden-never-charged-911-inside-job-likely-210784|title=Osama Bin Laden never charged for 911 - Inside Job likely|publisher=International Business Times|date=2011-05-02|accessdate=2017-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170529001402/http://www.ibtimes.com/osama-bin-laden-never-charged-911-inside-job-likely-210784|archive-date=2017-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wapo2006">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/27/AR2006082700687.html|title=Bin Laden, Most Wanted For Embassy Bombings?|publisher=The Washington Post|date=2006-08-28|accessdate=2017-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411135133/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/27/AR2006082700687.html|archive-date=2017-04-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/wanted_terrorists/usama-bin-laden|title=Most Wanted Terrorists • USAMA BIN LADEN|publisher=FBI|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526174037/https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/wanted_terrorists/usama-bin-laden|archivedate=2016-05-26|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2015-12-20}}</ref>2011年本·拉登被殺後，FBI在其官方網站表示本·拉登是九一一襲擊的主謀。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fbi.gov/news/stories/bin-laden-killed |title=Bin Laden Killed — FBI |access-date=2017-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170521054208/https://www.fbi.gov/news/stories/bin-laden-killed |archive-date=2017-05-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* 2006年9月，[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]公布基地組織的紀錄片，拍攝911劫機犯Hamza al-Ghamdi和Wail al-Shehri準備劫機的過程。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2006/09/07/al-qaeda-tape.html |title=Bin Laden 9/11 planning video aired |publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |date=2006-09-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013183902/http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2006/09/07/al-qaeda-tape.html |archivedate=2007-10-13 |accessdate=2011-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

