* [[2011年利比亚内战|2011年利比亚内战]]導致卡扎菲政權勢危，[[卡扎菲|卡扎菲]]指责基地组织是利比亚危机的幕后策划者，其目的是想在利比亚建立伊斯兰王国。而利比亞反政府武裝成員在接受西方媒体采访时，只承认他們內部的確有人來自基地組織。<ref name="AQ1">{{cite web | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8407047/Libyan-rebel-commander-admits-his-fighters-have-al-Qaeda-links.html | title = Libyan rebel commander admits his fighters have al-Qaeda links | work = The Telegraph | date = 2011-03-25 | accessdate = 2011-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110327223154/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8407047/Libyan-rebel-commander-admits-his-fighters-have-al-Qaeda-links.html | archive-date = 2011-03-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="AQ2">{{cite web | url = http://news.qq.com/a/20110327/000244.htm | title = 利比亚叛军首领承认招募基地组织武装分子 | work = 腾讯新闻 | date = 2011-03-27 | accessdate = 2011-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309115906/http://news.qq.com/a/20110327/000244.htm | archive-date = 2016-03-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
